OL,7,FSinn Fein vice president Michelle
OL,8,FO'Neill has apologised for "hurt and
OL,9,Fdistress" after two press officers
OL,10,Fprovided references for a former
OL,11,Femployee under investigation for child
OL,12,Fsex offences.
OL,14,FShe reiterated her "anger and disgust"
OL,15,Fthat the two former press officers at
OL,16,FStormont provided references for
OL,17,FMichael McMonagle for a job with the
OL,18,FBritish Heart Foundation (BHF).
