OL,7,FLast month, McMonagle, 42, from
OL,8,FLimewood Street, Londonderry, admitted
OL,9,Fa series of offences, including
OL,10,Fattempting to incite a child to engage
OL,11,Fin sexual activity.
OL,13,FSinn Fein has been facing questions
OL,14,Fover how it handled the matter.
OL,16,FMs O'Neill and head of the BHF in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Fearghal McKinney
OL,18,Fspoke earlier on Saturday about the
OL,19,Ffall-out from the case.
