OL,7,FMcMonagle was first arrested in August
OL,8,F2021.
OL,10,FSinn Fein has said it suspended him as
OL,11,Fsoon as it became aware of the police
OL,12,Finvestigation and his employment was
OL,13,Fterminated in June 2022 when his
OL,14,Fcontract ended.
OL,16,FHe went on to work for BHF from
OL,17,FSeptember 2022.
