OL,7,FMs O'Neill also revealed that she
OL,8,Festablished on Thursday that in August
OL,9,F2023, following media reports of
OL,10,Fcharges against McMonagle, BHF
OL,11,Fcontacted Sinn Fein's former HR
OL,12,Fmanager to verify the email address
OL,13,Fand identity of the senior press
OL,14,Fofficer who had provided the reference
OL,15,Fthe previous year, which the HR
OL,16,Fmanager did.
