OL,7,FShe said this contact from the BHF was
OL,8,Fnot brought to her attention, or the
OL,9,Fattention of the Sinn Fein leadership,
OL,10,Fat that time, which she termed "a
OL,11,Fserious omission".
OL,13,F"Michael McMonagle's actions are
OL,14,Futterly reprehensible and he is being
OL,15,Fheld fully accountable under the law.
OL,16,FHis crimes have inflicted significant
OL,17,Fharm on his innocent victims. There is
OL,18,Fnothing more reprehensible than the
OL,19,Fabuse of a child," she said.
