OL,7,FMs O'Neill said she was made aware of
OL,8,Fhis suspension and had no further
OL,9,Fcontact with him.
OL,11,FShe was pictured at an event which
OL,12,FMcMonagle had attended in Parliament
OL,13,FBuildings in February 2023.
OL,15,FMs O'Neill reiterated that she had not
OL,16,Fbeen aware he was at the event, adding
OL,17,Fshe "had no knowledge that he had
OL,18,Fgained employment with the British
OL,19,FHeart Foundation".
