OL,7,FShe apologised on behalf of Sinn Fein
OL,8,Ffor the actions of the press officers.
OL,10,F"On Wednesday September 25, 2024, Sinn
OL,11,FFein and I were informed that two
OL,12,Fpress officers, who were former
OL,13,Fcolleagues of Michael McMonagle, had
OL,14,Fprovided employment references for
OL,15,Fhim," she said.
OL,26,@lD@BrrrD@AOUwD@EO]
