OL,7,F"I am absolutely appalled and
OL,8,Fhorrified that this occurred. These
OL,9,Freferences were given without the
OL,10,Fknowledge or authorisation of the
OL,11,Fparty. Under no circumstances would
OL,12,Fthe party provide a reference, for
OL,13,Fwork or otherwise, for Michael
OL,14,FMcMonagle.
OL,16,F"On behalf of Sinn Fein, I apologise
OL,17,Ffor the hurt and distress caused by
OL,18,Ftheir actions."
OL,26,@lD@BrroD@AOUxD@AOUzD@OO]
