OL,7,FShe added: "This morning, I spoke with
OL,8,FFearghal McKinney, head of the British
OL,9,FHeart Foundation NI, to discuss this
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,F"This is an organisation that does
OL,13,Fgreat work providing support, research
OL,14,Fand advocacy services. I am deeply
OL,15,Fsorry that they have been caught up in
OL,16,Fthis unacceptable situation.
OL,18,F"I look forward to a continued
OL,19,Fconstructive relationship with the
OL,20,FBritish Heart Foundation in promoting
OL,21,Fheart health.
