OL,7,F"Sinn Fein will be issuing
OL,8,Finstructions to all managers and
OL,9,Fmembers of staff regarding future
OL,10,Frequests for character references.
OL,12,F"As a political leader and a mother, I
OL,13,Fwant to be clear that the issue of
OL,14,Fchild safeguarding is of paramount
OL,15,Fimportance to me. The Sinn Fein
OL,16,Fleadership and I will ensure that a
OL,17,Fsituation like this will never arise
OL,18,Fagain."
