OL,7,FHe added: "Michelle O'Neill agreed
OL,8,Frecent comments by her and party
OL,9,Fcolleagues questioning the BHF's due
OL,10,Fdiligence process were unhelpful and
OL,11,Fshe expressed regret for the damage
OL,12,Fand upset this has caused to our
OL,13,Fdedicated staff and supporters.
